	 <title>System.Count</title> 
	 <para></para> 
	 <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Remarks</bridgehead> 
	 <para>This is an aggregate operator that returns the number of rows in the
		  current group.</para> 
	 <example> 
		  <title>Example</title> 
		  <programlisting>select Employee group add {Count() Count};</programlisting> 
		  <programlisting>Count
-----
6</programlisting> 
	 </example> 
